  "core_payload": {
    "content_type": "markdown",
    "content": "# Roadmap Planner Agent\n\n## 1. Role\nRoadmap Planner Agent will become a more dynamic strategic planner capable of branch-aware sequencing, scenario comparison, and adaptation under uncertainty without degrading roadmap readability.\n\n## 2. Future Strategic Contract\nThe agent will shape stronger phase design across 30/60/90, 365-day, and 1000-day horizons, maintain roadmap variants for exploration versus delivery, and feed Planning Horizon Engine with strategic structures that remain intelligible under risk and change.\n\n## 3. Operational Consequence\nN1Hub will keep long-range coherence under pressure because roadmap structure, review pressure, tracker evidence, and execution uncertainty will remain connected instead of drifting apart.\n\n## 4. Philosophical Alignment\nRoadmap Planner Agent supports To Dig Deep by keeping long-horizon strategy explicit, branch-aware, and compressible into grounded execution."
  },
